'''锡纳罗亚贩毒集团'''（{{lang-es|Cártel de Sinaloa}}，'''CDS'''）<ref>{{cite news|title=Sinaloa Cartel Influence is Steadily Growing In Tijuana|url=http://www.borderlandbeat.com/2011/02/sinaloa-cartel-influence-is-steadily.html|newspaper=[[Borderland_Beat|Borderland Beat]]|date=23 February 2011|accessdate=2013-07-21|archive-date=2016-01-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160123170056/http://www.borderlandbeat.com/2011/02/sinaloa-cartel-influence-is-steadily.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>是一个总部位于[[墨西哥|墨西哥]][[锡纳罗亚州|锡纳罗亚州]][[库利亚坎|库利亚坎]]的犯罪集团，从事贩毒和洗钱等犯罪活动<ref>{{cite news|title=Mexico's Sinaloa gang grows empire, defies crackdown|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/01/19/us-mexico-drugs-idUSTRE70I6UZ20110119|accessdate=18 September 2011|newspaper=Reuters|date=19 January 2011|archive-date=2015-01-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150115012632/http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/01/19/us-mexico-drugs-idUSTRE70I6UZ20110119|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，活动范围包括[[下加利福尼亚州|下加利福尼亚州]]、[[杜兰戈州|杜兰戈州]]、[[索诺拉州|索诺拉州]]和[[奇瓦瓦州|奇瓦瓦州]]<ref name="Wilson">{{cite book|last=Freeman|first=Laurie|title=State of Siege:Drug-Related Violence and Corruption in Mexico|publisher=Woodrow Wilson International Center for Scholars|pages=7, 13, 15|url=http://www.wilsoncenter.org/news/docs/State_of_Siege_WOLA.pdf|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20061104023412/http://www.wilsoncenter.org/news/docs/State_of_Siege_WOLA.pdf|archivedate=2006-11-04}}</ref><ref name="Organized">{{cite book|last=Bailey|first=John J.|coauthors=Roy Godson|title=Organized Crime and Democratic Governability: Mexico and the U.S.-Mexican Borderlands|publisher=Univ of Pittsburgh Press|year=2000|page=146|isbn=0-8229-5758-2}}</ref>。这一集团还被称作'''古兹曼-洛埃拉集团'''、'''太平洋贩毒集团'''（因为该集团来自墨西哥太平洋海岸）、'''联盟'''或'''血联盟'''<ref name="Wilson"/><ref>{{es icon}} {{cite news|title=El cártel de Sinaloa, una alianza de sangre|url=http://www.eluniversal.com.mx/nacion/179403.html|accessdate=20 June 2012|newspaper=El Universal|date=30 July 2010|archive-date=2015-01-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150114003937/http://www.eluniversal.com.mx/nacion/179403.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Blames">{{cite news|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/latestCrisis/idUSN07300830|title=Mexico blames Gulf cartel for surge in drug murders|last=Rama|first=Anahi|date=7 April 2008|publisher=Reuters|accessdate=2008-04-11|archive-date=2019-09-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190929155231/https://www.reuters.com/article/latestCrisis/idUSN07300830|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="100k">{{cite news|url=http://www.washingtontimes.com/news/2009/mar/03/100000-foot-soldiers-in-cartels/|title=100,000 foot soldiers in Mexican cartels|last=Carter|first=Sara A.|date=3 March 2009|publisher=The Washington Times|accessdate=2009-03-03|archive-date=2015-10-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151016083017/http://www.washingtontimes.com/news/2009/mar/03/100000-foot-soldiers-in-cartels/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。当贝尔特兰-莱瓦兄弟分离出去时，“联盟”在一定程度上被拆分了<ref name="LastNarco">{{cite book|last=Beith|first=Malcolm|title=The Last Narco|year=2010|publisher=Grove Press|isbn=978-0-8021-1952-0|pages=|url=http://www.amazon.com/Last-Narco-Inside-Worlds-Wanted/dp/0802119522|access-date=2013-07-21|archive-date=2017-09-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170927135957/https://www.amazon.com/Last-Narco-Inside-Worlds-Wanted/dp/0802119522|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

[[美国情报体系|美国情报体系]]将锡纳罗亚贩毒集团认定为“全世界势力最为庞大的贩毒集团”<ref>{{cite news|title=U.S. Intelligence Says Sinaloa Cartel Has Won Battle for Ciudad Juarez Drug Routes|url=http://www.cnsnews.com/node/63984|newspaper=CNS News|date=9 April 2010|accessdate=2013-07-21|archive-date=2021-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210305234219/https://cnsnews.com/node/63984|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2011年，《[[洛杉矶时报|洛杉矶时报]]》称之为“墨西哥势力最庞大的犯罪集团”<ref>{{cite news|title=Unraveling Mexico's Sinaloa drug cartel|url=http://articles.latimes.com/2011/jul/24/local/la-me-cartel-20110724|newspaper=Los Angeles Times|date=24 July 2011|first=Richard|last=Marosi|accessdate=2013-07-21|archive-date=2011-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110924054008/http://articles.latimes.com/2011/jul/24/local/la-me-cartel-20110724|dead-url=no}}</ref>。该贩毒集团与“[[金三角|金三角]]”一词相关，这缘于他们主要活动的锡纳罗亚、杜兰戈及奇瓦瓦三州，而这一地区是墨西哥主要的[[鸦片|鸦片]]和[[大麻|大麻]]生产地<ref name="LastNarco"/>。据[[美国司法部长|美国司法部长]]称，在1990年—2008年期间，锡纳罗亚贩毒集团总共运输和销售入美国近200吨的[[可卡因|可卡因]]及大量的[[海洛因|海洛因]]<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2009/08/20/AR2009082001958.html|title=U.S. charges 10 accused Mexican drug cartel leaders|work=Reuters|publisher=The Washington Post|accessdate=2009-08-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120331074421/http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2009/08/20/AR2009082001958.html|archive-date=2012-03-31|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

2014年2月22日，該集團領導人[[华金·古兹曼|华金·古兹曼]](Joaquin Guzman)於[[马萨特兰|马萨特兰]]被捕[http://news.163.com/photoview/00AO0001/43181.html] {{Wayback|url=http://news.163.com/photoview/00AO0001/43181.html |date=20190226111341 }}<ref >{{cite web |url=http://news.sohu.com/20140223/n395496163.shtml |language= |title=墨西哥头号通缉要犯大毒枭古兹曼在该国被捕 |publisher=中国新闻网 |date=2014年2月23日 |accessdate= |archive-date=2019年2月26日 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190226111310/http://news.sohu.com/20140223/n395496163.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但在2015年成功越狱，他被认为是全球最大的毒枭，之前美国悬赏500万美元缉捕他，他也是肆虐墨西哥境内多年的众多毒品暴力的幕后主使，2011年6月被《[[富比士|富比士]]》列为“全球十大恶人榜”首位<ref >{{cite web |url=http://world.163.com/14/0223/07/9LOI98MQ0001121M.html |language= |title=全球最大毒枭落网 致3.8万人死成“全球首恶” |publisher=中国新闻网 |date=2014-02-23 |accessdate= |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140301100303/http://world.163.com/14/0223/07/9LOI98MQ0001121M.html |archive-date=2014-03-01 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。古兹曼在2016年再次被墨西哥政府逮捕并于2017年被引渡至美国，目前被关押在美国纽约的联邦监狱，而锡那罗亚集团则由古兹曼的三个儿子接手管理。

